  "texts": [
    "In contrast, high-performance SCMs like SF and MK provide superior strength properties but are more expensive and energy-intensive to produce.",
    "The selection of SCMs should consider project goals, cost-effectiveness, and environmental impact, balancing affordability and performance based on specific requirements. 8.",
    "The use of SCMs comes with some limitations, including variability in quality and availability.",
    "For example, changes in environmental regulations have affected the composition of FA.",
    "The reactivity of SCMs also depends on their chemical and physical properties, which can vary significantly between sources."
